          <ul class="catalog-notes">
              <li>Winter</li>
              <li>Prerequisite: One course in Anthropology, Geography or Environmental Studies, Introductory Biology, or permission of the instructor.</li>
              <li>Restriction: Students must have completed at least two full semesters at their home university. Only open to students in the Canadian Field Studies in Africa program.</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

  </div> <!-- /.node -->
              </div>
